OL,3,CBirmingham homeowners fight to save
OL,4,Cproperties from #1bn regeneration
OL,6,FHomeowners in Birmingham's Druids
OL,7,FHeath say they are determined to save
OL,8,Ftheir properties from demolition as
OL,9,Fpart of a #1 billion regeneration
OL,10,Fproject.
OL,12,FThe city council plans to replace
OL,13,F1,800 homes on the post-war estate
OL,14,Fwith 3,500 new ones. However, some
OL,15,Fresidents are refusing to move and say
OL,16,Fthey will resist any compulsory
OL,17,Fpurchase orders.
