OL,3,CBirmingham homeowners fight to save
OL,4,Cproperties from #1bn regeneration
OL,6,FJayne Harper, who has lived in her
OL,7,Fhome for 38 years with her husband
OL,8,FMick, said: "I can't explain it. It's
OL,9,Fjust home. And I'm so comfortable
OL,10,Fhere. I don't see why the council
OL,11,Fshould come along and treat us like a
OL,12,Fbox of Lego, breaking us down and
OL,13,Frebuilding us again. We don't need it."
OL,15,FMick Harper added: "I'm an Englishman,
OL,16,Fmy home is my castle."
OL,18,FThe council argues that the area has
OL,19,Fdeteriorated and is in need of
OL,20,Finvestment.
