OL,6,FWork on the regeneration could begin
OL,7,Fin 2027, with the project expected to
OL,8,Ftake place over five phases spanning
OL,9,Ftwo decades.
OL,11,FCouncillor Jane Francis, Cabinet
OL,12,FMember for Housing and Homelessness,
OL,13,Fsaid: "We understand that people's
OL,14,Fhomes are central to their lives. Any
OL,15,Fregeneration will bring big changes
OL,16,Fthat will cause understandable
OL,17,Fdistress for those affected.
