OL,11,F"We recognise these feelings and so we
OL,12,Fhave worked closely with the community
OL,13,Fover the past few years to reassure
OL,14,Fthem, answer questions, and to develop
OL,15,Fa masterplan for the regeneration of
OL,16,FDruids Heath - one that meets the
OL,17,Fneeds of the people who live and work
OL,18,Fthere.
