OL,6,F"To support residents, independent
OL,7,Fadvisors have been appointed to advise
OL,8,Fhomeowners throughout the process.
OL,9,FFrom spring, independent advisors will
OL,10,Fbe on site with council officers so
OL,11,Fpeople can drop in and ask any
OL,12,Fquestions they may have."
OL,14,FThe council says the redevelopment
OL,15,Fwill provide energy-efficient homes,
OL,16,Fgreen spaces, new transport links, and
OL,17,Fcommunity facilities.
