OL,6,FIt has also promised that those who
OL,7,Fwant to remain in the area will be
OL,8,Fgiven the opportunity to do so, with
OL,9,Fefforts to minimise disruption by
OL,10,Fensuring residents only need to move
OL,11,Fonce.
OL,13,FResidents say they have been told they
OL,14,Fwill receive market value for their
OL,15,Fhomes plus 10%. However, they are
OL,16,Fconcerned that years of uncertainty
OL,17,Fhave already lowered house prices,
OL,18,Freducing the amount they will
OL,19,Fultimately receive.
