OL,6,FWhile they will be able to move into
OL,7,Fone of the new properties, it would
OL,8,Flikely be through a shared ownership
OL,9,Fscheme - something that does not
OL,10,Fappeal to those who currently own
OL,11,Ftheir homes outright.
OL,13,FThe council says a survey has shown
OL,14,Fbroad support for the regeneration.
OL,15,FHowever, some residents remain
OL,16,Funconvinced.
OL,18,FFor many, the process now feels
OL,19,Finevitable. Some of Druids Heath's
OL,20,Fdecaying tower blocks already stand
OL,21,Fempty.
