OL,3,CBirmingham homeowners fight to save
OL,4,Cproperties from #1bn regeneration
OL,6,FAnd the plans are not limited to this
OL,7,Festate. The city council has also
OL,8,Foutlined similar redevelopment
OL,9,Fproposals for areas such as Ladywood.
OL,11,FBirmingham is expected to see
OL,12,Fsignificant population growth in the
OL,13,Fcoming years, with the city needing to
OL,14,Fbuild more than 100,000 homes over the
OL,15,Fnext two decades.
OL,17,FResidents in Druids Heath remain
OL,18,Fanxious about what the changes will
OL,19,Fmean for them as they await further
OL,20,Fdetails on the future of their homes.
